object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct claim_Stg.SystemId, claim_Stg.Id, claim_Stg.ClaimNumber, claim_Stg.LossCauseCd, claim_Stg.LossDt, claim_Stg.ReportedDt,
 claim_Stg.CatastropheRef, claim_Stg.StatusCd, claim_Stg.PolicyNumber,
 case when len(claim_stg.policyversion)='1' then concat('00',claim_stg.policyversion)
             when len(claim_stg.policyversion)='2' then concat('0',claim_stg.policyversion)
             else claim_stg.policyversion end as PolicyVersion, claim_Stg.PolicyRiskIdRef,claim_Stg.JurisdictionStateCd, claim_Stg.ClaimType, claim_Stg.ExaminerProviderRef,
claim_stg.SubrogationInd, claim_Stg.SubLossCauseCd, claim_Stg.DOIComplaintInd, claim_Stg.InSIUInd, claim_Stg.SIUStatus, claim_Stg.StatusDt, claim_Stg.NoPaymentReason, claim_Stg.AddDt, claim_Stg.StormHurricaneName, claim_Stg.ForRecordOnlyInd, 
claim_Stg.TypeCd,
claim_Stg.ReportedBy,
claim_Stg.ReportedTo,
claim_Stg.LossNoticeNumber,
claim_Stg.SuitFiledInd
FROM
 dbo.claim_Stg

object.customQuery: SELECT ClaimDetail.ClaimKey as ClaimKey, ClaimDetail.ClaimSystemId as ClaimSystemId, ClaimDetail.ClaimId as ClaimId, ClaimDetail.LosscauseCd as LosscauseCd, ClaimDetail.LosscauseDesc as LosscauseDesc, ClaimDetail.LossDt as LossDt, ClaimDetail.LossReportedDt as LossReportedDt, ClaimDetail.CatastropheRef as CatastropheRef, ClaimDetail.CatGroupDesc as CatGroupDesc, ClaimDetail.ClaimStatusCd as ClaimStatusCd, ClaimDetail.PolicyRiskIdRef as PolicyRiskIdRef, ClaimDetail.ClaimHashKey as ClaimHashKey, ClaimDetail.RowEffStrtDt as RowEffStrtDt, ClaimDetail.RowEffEndDt as RowEffEndDt, ClaimDetail.PolicyKey as PolicyKey, ClaimDetail.ClaimNumber as ClaimNumber FROM dbo.ClaimDetail  where ClaimDetail.RowEffEndDt='9999-12-31 00:00:00.0000000'

object.customQuery:
SELECT a.SystemId as SystemId, a.CMMContainer as CMMContainer, a.Id as Id, a.StatusCd as StatusCd,
  a.Description as Description, a.SubrogationStatusCd as SubrogationStatusCd, a.StatuteDt as StatuteDt,
   a.OpenedDt as OpenedDt, a.ClosedDt as ClosedDt, a.DeductibleWaivedInd as DeductibleWaivedInd, 
   a.SubrogationProviderRef as SubrogationProviderRef, a.InstallmentPaymentInd as InstallmentPaymentInd, 
   a.ResponsiblePartyLiabilityPct as ResponsiblePartyLiabilityPct, a.RespPartyPreferDeliveryMethod as RespPartyPreferDeliveryMethod, 
   a.RespOwnerPreferDeliveryMethod as RespOwnerPreferDeliveryMethod, a.InstallmentAmount as InstallmentAmount,
    a.TotalRecoveryAmt as TotalRecoveryAmt, a.FirstDueDate as FirstDueDate, a.SubrogationProviderNo as SubrogationProviderNo,
	 a.ResponsiblePartyIntlInd as ResponsiblePartyIntlInd, a.ResponsibleOwnerIntlInd as ResponsibleOwnerIntlInd,
	  a.AdverseCarrierInternationalInd as AdverseCarrierInternationalInd,
  a.Demand as Demand, a.RowId as RowId, a.ParentId as ParentId FROM dbo.subrogation_stg a(nolock)
  left join dbo.claim_stg b(nolock) on 
 a.parentid=b.id where a.subrogationstatuscd='Open' and b.typecd='Claim'----

object.customQuery: SELECT catastrophe.CatastropheNumber as CatastropheNumber, catastrophe.Description as Description, catastrophe.SystemId as SystemId FROM catastrophe--

SELECT nm.CommercialName as CommercialName, nm.IndexName as IndexName, clm.SystemId as SystemId, p.ProviderTypeCd as ProviderTypeCd 
FROM dbo.claimant_stg clm
join dbo.assignedprovider_stg ap
on ap.systemid=clm.systemid
and clm.id=ap.parentid
join dbo.provider_stg p
on p.systemid=ap.providerref
join dbo.nameinfo_stg nm
on nm.systemid=p.systemid
and nm.cmmcontainer='Provider'
where assignedprovidertypecd like 'AssignedOther%'
and nametypecd='ProviderName'

object.customQuery:
SELECT nf.commercialname as CommercialName, clm.systemid as SystemId, la.associateTypecd as AssociateTypeCd FROM
dbo.claim_stg clm inner join dbo.litigationassociate_stg la
on clm.systemid=la.systemid
join dbo.partyinfo_stg pf
on la.id=pf.parentid
and clm.systemid=pf.systemid
join dbo.nameinfo_stg nf
on pf.id=nf.parentid
and clm.systemid=nf.systemid where la.StatusCd='Active' --

object.customQuery:
SELECT Max(ClaimDetail.ClaimReopenInd) as ClaimReopenInd, Max(ClaimDetail.ClaimReopenDt) as ClaimReopenDt, ClaimDetail.ClaimSystemId as ClaimSystemId FROM dbo.ClaimDetail
Where ClaimDetail.ClaimReopenInd is NOT NULL
group by ClaimDetail.ClaimSystemId--

object.customQuery:
SELECT task_stg.TemplateId as TemplateId, 
task_stg.Name as Name, 
task_stg.AddedByUserId as AddedByUserId, 
task_stg.Status as Status, 
task_stg.AddDt as AddDt, 
task_stg.CurrentOwner as CurrentOwner, 
tl.Id as TasklinkId, 
tl.ModelName as TasklinkModelName, 
clm.Systemid as ClaimSystemid 
FROM
 dbo.task_stg task_stg inner join  dbo.tasklink_stg tl 
on tl.systemid=task_stg.systemid
and tl.parentid=task_stg.id
inner join dbo.Claim_stg clm
on clm.systemid=tl.idref
and modelname='Claim'
where clm.typecd='Lossnotice'
and templateid in ('LossNoticeTask2004','LossNoticeTask2001')

object.customQuery:
SELECT AddDt as AddDt, RowId as RowId, CMMContainer as CMMContainer, Id as Id, UpdateCount as UpdateCount, UpdateUser as UpdateUser, UpdateTimestamp as UpdateTimestamp,
 IdRef as IdRef, TemplateId as TemplateId, Description as Description, Filename as Filename, OriginalFilename as OriginalFilename, Memo as Memo, Status as Status, 
 AddTm as AddTm, AddUser as AddUser, UpdateDt as UpdateDt, UpdateTm as UpdateTm, HasAnnotationsInd as HasAnnotationsInd, TransactionNumber as TransactionNumber,
  SourceRef as SourceRef, SourceContainerName as SourceContainerName, SystemId as SystemId, ParentId as ParentId  from 
(SELECT AddDt as AddDt, RowId as RowId, CMMContainer as CMMContainer, Id as Id, UpdateCount as UpdateCount, UpdateUser as UpdateUser, UpdateTimestamp as UpdateTimestamp,
 IdRef as IdRef, TemplateId as TemplateId, Description as Description, Filename as Filename, OriginalFilename as OriginalFilename, Memo as Memo, Status as Status, 
 AddTm as AddTm, AddUser as AddUser, UpdateDt as UpdateDt, UpdateTm as UpdateTm, HasAnnotationsInd as HasAnnotationsInd, TransactionNumber as TransactionNumber,
  SourceRef as SourceRef, SourceContainerName as SourceContainerName, SystemId as SystemId, ParentId as ParentId ,
  row_number() over(partition by systemid,parentid order by adddt ) as rn  from dbo.attachment_stg(nolock) where cmmcontainer='Claim') a where a.rn=1  ----

object.customQuery:
select PolicyKey as  PolicyKey,ClaimNumber as ClaimNumber,max(CoverageCd) as CoverageCd from (
SELECT ClaimTransaction.CoverageCd 
, ClaimTransaction.PolicyKey 
, ClaimTransaction.ClaimNumber 
FROM dbo.ClaimTransaction
Where roweffenddt>getdate()
union all
select CoverageCd as CoverageCd
, PolicyNumber+PolicyVersion as PolicyKey
, ClaimNumber as ClaimNumber
FROM dbo.Claimstats_Stg
)t Group by PolicyKey,ClaimNumber
